Risk of losing chat history on new update. Support is useless. WhatsApp no longer looks for local backups if there is no Drive backup or if Drive restore fails. If you use Google drive all media, pictures and videos show as today's date. So, smart users save a local backup in a zip file so file dates are preserved on new install. Whatsapp no longer lets you restore from a local database file. Many reddit posts on how Google Drive backup has failed and chat history has been lost. Issue ignored
